Title: Empirical Study of Change-Prone and Fault-Prone Method Prediction Focusing on Comment Ownership
UseOF-SZZ: identify bug fixes, when bug-fix-related keywords or bug IDs appeared in commitment log
Summary: to understand the relationship between the developer and their code and its contribution to change-prone and/or fault-prone method prediction
Outcome: The results confirmed the significant influence of OCCR for predicting changes and faults in methods.
